SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the Species at Risk Act (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisOrder amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE SPECIES AT RISK ACT (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in accordance with the Committee on the Status of Endangered Wildlife in Canada's (COSEWIC) recommended name changes for 34 species in order to either to change the scientific name, or common name (or both) of these species.
